{"type":"text","timestamp":1775896768476,"sessionID":"ses_28453c10fffeNT2KVEuElwpEgY","part":{"id":"prt_d7bb20d07001OmDuygJTIQP5nR","messageID":"msg_d7bb1d7ba001F7eZHdJ4OxaoW2","sessionID":"ses_28453c10fffeNT2KVEuElwpEgY","type":"text","text":"The proposal.md for AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 has been successfully created. The document includes:\n\n## Summary\n\n**Structure:**\n- **Purpose**: Centralized metadata management for the AgentCube CLI lifecycle\n- **Scope**: In-scope (AgentMetadata model, MetadataOptions dataclass, MetadataService) and out-of-scope items\n- **Design**: Class structures, flow diagrams for loading/saving/validation\n- **Impact Analysis**: Affected components (all Runtime classes) and data format changes\n- **Alternatives Considered**: JSON vs YAML, TOML, SQLite, Dataclasses vs Pydantic, etc.\n- **Verification**: Complete code examples for all functionality\n- **References**: Related specs and documentation\n- **Success Criteria**: 23 verification checkpoints\n\n**Key Components Covered:**\n1. **`AgentMetadata`** Pydantic model with 20+ fields and validators\n2. **`MetadataOptions`** dataclass for CLI overrides\n3. **`MetadataService`** with load/save/update/validate operations\n4. **YAML persistence** with fallback loading (agent_metadata.yaml → agent.yaml → metadata.yaml)\n5. **Schema validation** for language, build_mode, and port\n6. **Workspace validation** for Python (*.py files) and Java (pom.xml)","time":{"start":1775896768473,"end":1775896768473}}}
